<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>厦门市文化和旅游局推出的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“2020中秋国庆厦门旅游网红打卡点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和线路征集评选”正式启动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200928/15dad5a727964f3baf32098ad121d5fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
